OL,3,CBoy, 13, charged with arson after
OL,4,Ccorner shop fire and homes evacuated
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been charged with
OL,7,Farson after a Nottingham corner shop
OL,8,Fwent up in flames, forcing residents
OL,9,Fof nearby properties to evacuate.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FRanya Grocery shop, on The Wells Road
OL,13,Fin St Ann's, just before 4 am on
OL,14,FSaturday morning, June 6, as a blaze
OL,15,Fengulfed the entire property.
OL,17,FThe fire had spread from the shop's
OL,18,Ffront entrance, at the junction with
OL,19,FRichmond Avenue, to the flat above,
OL,20,Fprompting residents to escape onto the
OL,21,Fstreet.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
