OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781269896
OL,3,CBoy, 13, charged with arson after
OL,4,Ccorner shop fire and homes evacuated
OL,6,FPeople living in other nearby
OL,7,Fproperties were also rescued by the
OL,8,Ffire service, who brought the blaze
OL,9,Funder control. A joint police and fire
OL,10,Finvestigation found the cause of the
OL,11,Ffire to be arson.
OL,13,FA suspect, a 13-year-old boy, was
OL,14,Flater arrested by officers and has now
OL,15,Fbeen charged with arson with intent to
OL,16,Fendanger life and arson with
OL,17,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,18,Fendangered.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781269896
OL,3,CBoy, 13, charged with arson after
OL,4,Ccorner shop fire and homes evacuated
OL,6,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,7,Freasons, has also been charged with
OL,8,Frobbery and possession of a knife in
OL,9,Fpublic following a separate incident
OL,10,Fat a shop in Strelley Road, also on
OL,11,FJune 6.
OL,13,FA shopkeeper was threatened with a
OL,14,Fknife before hundreds of pounds worth
OL,15,Fof items were stolen. He has also been
OL,16,Fcharged with one count of shop theft
OL,17,Fafter items were stolen from a
OL,18,Fsupermarket in Green Lane on May 9.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
