PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1781269896
OL,3,CBoy, 13, charged with arson after
OL,4,Ccorner shop fire and homes evacuated
OL,6,FThe boy appeared at Nottingham
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, June
OL,8,F10th, and will next appear at the same
OL,9,Fcourt on June 22.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Nigel Malik, of
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "Any
OL,13,Farson attack is extremely reckless and
OL,14,Fthis fire was lit in a shop adjoining
OL,15,Fa number of neighbouring homes.
OL,17,F"We know the incident caused concern
OL,18,Fin the neighbourhood, so I hope people
OL,19,Fwelcome the emergency services'
OL,20,Fresponse and these charges.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
